				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: why is my mana take so long to fill?<a name="51159"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 10 04 9:39 PM</span></td>
