				<td colspan="2"><span>Forgot to mention there is a great way to get unlimited mana regen... sort of...depending on what you're doing.
<br />

<br />
You mentioned charm. I'm guessing she's swarm kiting. If she is swarm kiting AND getting good exp AND have access to a cleric consider her killing herself when she is OoM. She will come back with enough mana to start swarming again. Then just before the first corps rezz timer is about to run out get a cleric to rezz her corps farm. Rince, repeat.
<br />

<br />
Only do this if she is getting enough exp between deaths to make it worth her effort and you can guarentee rezzes.</span></td>
